graph TB
    subgraph "FMS Guardrails Ecosystem"
        Orchestrator["FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>(upstream caller)"]
    end

    subgraph "Guardrails Regex Detector"
        direction TB
        HealthEndpoint["/health<br/>GET 8080/TCP"]
        DetectionEndpoint["/api/v1/text/contents<br/>POST 8080/TCP"]

        subgraph "Detection Engine"
            direction LR
            BuiltInPatterns["Built-in PII Patterns<br/>email, ssn, credit-card"]
            CustomRegex["Custom Regex<br/>arbitrary patterns via request"]
            RegexEngine["Rust regex Engine<br/>regex 1.11.1"]
        end

        DetectionEndpoint -->|invokes| RegexEngine
        BuiltInPatterns -->|compiled into| RegexEngine
        CustomRegex -->|compiled into| RegexEngine
    end

    subgraph "Runtime"
        Tokio["Tokio Async Runtime<br/>(multi-threaded)"]
        Axum["Axum HTTP Framework<br/>0.7.9"]
        TowerHTTP["tower-http<br/>Request Tracing"]
        Tracing["tracing / tracing-subscriber<br/>Structured Logging"]
    end

    Orchestrator -->|POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP| DetectionEndpoint
    DetectionEndpoint -->|DetectionResponse<br/>start/end offsets, type, score| Orchestrator

    Axum -->|serves| HealthEndpoint
    Axum -->|serves| DetectionEndpoint
    Tokio -->|powers| Axum
    TowerHTTP -->|middleware for| Axum
    Tracing -->|logging for| Axum

    style Orchestrator fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style HealthEndpoint fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style DetectionEndpoint fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style BuiltInPatterns fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CustomRegex fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RegexEngine fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Tokio fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Axum fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style TowerHTTP fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Tracing fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
